{"tid":1347012,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲仔無屋企返","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T10:36:28.000Z","uid":135406,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"110a5e0b4699295775eceb027185363b15709db6","tid":1347012,"uid":135406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"小弟屋企人係深藍奶共廢老，又固執又自大又無知，嘈都嘈過好多次，基本上已經係無撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次發夢完返到屋企都一定會嘈大交，係出面食蛋捱棍，返到屋企以為有得抖下結果仲要比兩隻廢老失撚晒控咁指住黎屌，嗰種感覺真係好難頂。<br />\n<br />\n所以想問下有冇巴絲有平租既地方可以比呢個乞衣仔訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，目前仲係學生但搬出黎一定會瘋狂做pt照顧好自己，再留低我真係驚有情緒病。<br />\ntg:Homelesshi"},{"pid":"0fb8da817f3698cbcd150d4d4df1897e0ef3a1fb","tid":1347012,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1193da0500c0a0e7331e73357c88b34b0cb0bad0","tid":1347012,"uid":68471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2450327688378864?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2450327688378864%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=2a314ae0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2450327688378864?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n0&rsquo;22 開始，香港人醒未？"},{"pid":"b33e1bfd757d75876ef0436eeae0253587e784c6","tid":1347012,"uid":182080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vmg9a83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmg9a83.png&h=11562fc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff5b6389cc02c1733971c7ed63820ff8